    "attributes": {
        "action": "Stop all smart motorways and re-instate all hard shoulders",
        "additional_details": "We think re-instating hard shoulders will help protect all motorway users and could also assist emergency services to get to an accident, breakdown or emergency sooner.",
        "background": "We want all motorways to have hard shoulders and safety refuge areas. The Government should abolish smart motorways, as we believe they are not safe. ",
